{"tid":363110,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"多蒙特ceo:巴塞經理話丹比利就加盟 應該係比皇馬打到傻撚左","createTime":"2017-08-17T11:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T15:22:04.000Z","uid":10338,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"533751bb4d6ac328002490756b6f39aa496a6d39","tid":363110,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:45:34.000Z","msg":"圍繞著多特小將丹比利的轉會鬧劇再度升級，面對巴塞經理施古拉在超級杯賽后的發言：&ldquo;我們已經接近（完成轉會了）&rdquo;，多蒙特ceo華斯基在接受《踢球者》採訪時表示：&ldquo;巴塞距離他們實現轉會的願望都沒有更近一毫米。&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;我沒法解釋施古拉說的那些東西，之所以這麼說的原因估計是他的球隊在超級杯裡被皇馬打懵了。&rdquo;華斯基補充到。"},{"pid":"aae2ab353777f7f80622198383dd29cdb21ae98c","tid":363110,"uid":18669,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:49:37.000Z","msg":"好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b82ed2373a9a8e59c53c511f4f57c3c4d610f4f","tid":363110,"uid":45335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:52:01.000Z","msg":"柒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf77c600048a8242a5c83dc109e4dd483a2e5b8","tid":363110,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90c0217ebd1be6b2735402f106912edecd06a6a","tid":363110,"uid":33660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T12:01:25.000Z","msg":"疤塞真係笑話黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca6c9d74051755077ea365864697ffe52a49159","tid":363110,"uid":12169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T12:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"affb2c0b33795360e84cede5a8d834febef2bb0f","tid":363110,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T12:13:10.000Z","msg":"英文link?"},{"pid":"a93a94e9db6c3df4a0cbe86c7c2348c08dc01d80","tid":363110,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T12:18:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英文link?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/842375/Ousmane-Dembele-Borussia-Dortmund-Barcelona-Transfer-News-Rumours-Gossip\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.express.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2F842375%2FOusmane-Dembele-Borussia-Dortmund-Barcelona-Transfer-News-Rumours-Gossip&d=963wBI5SM1HAvGOLyy79mRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=c38c4e6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/842375/Ousmane-Dembele-Borussia-Dortmund-Barcelona-Transfer-News-Rumours-Gossip</a><br />\nBut Watzke has rubbished Segura&rsquo;s comments, claiming they are no closer to signing Dembele than when they first made contact with Dortmund.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;It is clear that Barcelona want to sign Ousmane Dembele, but they have not approached one millimetre,&quot; Watzke told Kicker.<br />\n<br />\nDembele has already been punished by Dortmund after failing to turn up to pre-season training as he looks to force through a move to Barca - and is said to be on strike in France.<br />\n<br />\nSegura was speaking after Barcelona&rsquo;s 5-1 aggregate defeat to Real Madrid in the Spanish Super Cup - and Watzke suggests the loss must have confused him.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;His intervention comes after the dizziness of Real Madrid in the Supercopa.&quot;"},{"pid":"1c6e76e9522fa19711075057834b095ba2898554","tid":363110,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T12:19:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5061d6fa4652a8b50dd750544c764ff3819078d1","tid":363110,"uid":36483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T12:20:47.000Z",